rows.label: qst100409_msg0002
rows.name:
This song is apparently popular in
Avaritia, mo! Do you know it, mo?

rows.label: qst100409_msg0003
rows.name: Oh, so it really is popular, mo!

rows.label: qst100409_msg0004
rows.name:
What's more, the restaurant's
specialty dish, Spicy Stra Lushi...

rows.label: qst100409_msg0005
rows.name:
Tastes just like home, like
your mother's cooking, mo!
Do you know it, mo?

rows.label: qst100409_msg0006
rows.name:
Momomo? Solala is the son of that
Singing-and-Cooking Falala person??

rows.label: qst100409_msg0007
rows.name:
Don't say such
irresponsible things, mo!

rows.label: qst100409_msg0008
rows.name:
Solala is a passionate Nopon
from the Kingdom of Invidia!

rows.label: qst100409_msg0009
rows.name: Not a greedy Nopon from Avaritia, mo!

rows.label: qst100409_msg0010
rows.name:
Could it be... you're trying to
kidnap Solala for his cuteness, mo?!

rows.label: qst100409_msg0011
rows.name:
Because Nopon are so fluffy
and cute, you're going to
sell me off, mo?!?!

rows.label: qst100409_msg0012
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Momomo~~! I'm being
kidnapped, mo! Help me, mo!

rows.label: qst100409_msg0013
rows.name: I'm escaping while I can, mo!!
